Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A case occurred at a popular magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A double trick mystery and mysterious events on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees one single truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He looks like a child, but thinks like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:47.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki Genyo's Magic Show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks so awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell right away that the poster is your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got that deathly cold vibe about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki Genyo's magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:02:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the snow-white Sanada Kazumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he uses a grim persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why would he want to meet you so urgently...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:20.78,Title,,0,0,0,,TRICK VS MAGIC\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki Genyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for making such a famous detective
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.92,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki Genyo (35)\NIllusionist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Fuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'm Mori Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the freeloader, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeloader?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told them that Fuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had called me, it was impossible to get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you like magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We often go to see shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I hadn't said so, they wouldn't have taken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You did that little thing with such an important look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm impressed with your technique, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Mori, I'll get straight to the point I called you in for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:04:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, a member of the team is trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you, Mouri, to find out who that person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did someone threaten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During rehearsals, a wooden beam fell on me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first time I thought it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone else around at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many other members besides you are on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the point of you asking questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, how many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides me, there are five people on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assistant Uehara Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:52.27,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Uehara Misa (26)\NAssistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I broke off my engagement with her 3 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she's still angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You broke off your engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also an assistant, Nakagawa Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:08.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nakagawa Chiaki (24)\NAssistant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We divorced by mutual agreement a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she still harbors resentment for my constant cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, responsible for the video, Ishida Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:19.13,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ishida Kazuma (19)\NVideo Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My favorite student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He makes videos and learns tricks at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Responsible for the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good and obedient boy with the rudiments of a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the only one I trust completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next to him is my director, Shoji Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:36.48,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shoji Shingo (37)\NDirector
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a former student of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he has no talent for magic, so I've hired him as my director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his views on the production are at odds with mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm going to ask him to leave after this performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're firing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in charge of mechanics, Hasegawa Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gambling enthusiast. He owes me a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:56.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hasegawa Minoru (45)\NResponsible for Mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I die, we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there's a motive for my murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excluding Ishida Kazuma, that's four suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. These are the tickets for the show tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not likely to happen during the performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there are life-threatening numbers on the program,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so let's pick a signal as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,rush to my aid, even during the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in that case, wouldn't it be better to cancel the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a professional illusionist, I have my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I too, as a professional detective, will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't let the team members know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still time before the show starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, are you disappointed in Mr. Fuyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he left a girl after the engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and divorced after many adulteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he talks about it as if it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more than that going on in the adult world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle has a lot going on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys go kill time somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a rule, accidents during a show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are usually caused by equipment.{something about magic tricks?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you dare ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Let's hide, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lie down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, isn't that the girls' sawing box?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's okay. They're just gonna connect afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pull up your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mori Kogoro? The detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like he hired him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think dumped them?{???}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to do it, you need to use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you and I teamed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would be simple and certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true the manager has a bad temper,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but isn't he the reason we have butter on our bread?{find alternative}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, you should be grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're only on his side because he lends you money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Kazuma, don't you really resent Fuyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he still won't let you go on stage as a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not offended at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care, but you should at least shave your beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look like a bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do they think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why should I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that trick, you have to lie on your back and press your knees to your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lie on your back and press your knees to your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how you saw the box without getting killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this incident, I realized that all\Nteam members have a motive to kill Fuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to look at the stunt equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the use of looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, welcome to the Fuyuki Genyo magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight you will enjoy some mysterious and inexplicable tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, she's enjoying herself after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, isn't it, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an excellent knife-thrower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki was only pretending to throw knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the knives were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just an impression. Thanks to a special device.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed it in the warehouse backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I was hiding with my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's showing a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are real spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone gets stabbed with these, it'll be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These straps are only held together by Velcro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After the curtain goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he'll escape to a small space on the edge of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's the famous detective Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} seemed to think the ladies had killed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he rushed over to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm alive, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I mustn't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second part will be life-threatening stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, a round of applause for Mr. Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki Genyo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to try it out to see if\NMr. Mori could see my signal properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you scare me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of this, I was humiliated in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what I said on stage was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the beginning of the second half, the dangerâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki, what was that trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stand that kind of screaming and blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at least not in my production.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to which, even the famous detective was fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I aspire to be full of excitement, dazzling and graceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, Shoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, the show won't be dazzling and graceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but rather a thrilling one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not exciting at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's just grotesque.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for this unpleasant scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone to the bathroom and hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off Mr. Fuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From here, I can move onto action at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, you can't watch from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When the curtain rises again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fuyuki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} will have to stand on the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki! Mr. Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remove the locks, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain! Lower the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasegawa! Lift the lid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ambulance! Ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, CPR.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fuyuki! Mr. Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to your senses, Fuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Fuyuki!
